API options:

Simple:
    - Method (GET/POST)
    - Parameters
    - Authentication (username/password)
    - Follow redirects (bool=false)
    
Advanced:
    - Extra headers (key=value pairs)
    - Verify SSL (bool=true)
    - Method (PUT/DELETE/PATCH/OPTIONS/HEAD)
    - Request body (form params, or a string)
    - Cookies
    
